ErpSearch
=========

ERP Search adds Solr extensions to Compass using Sunspot.


Example
=======

Start Solr server:
rake sunspot:solr:start

Index Content:
rake sunspot:reindex_content

Index Parties:
rake sunspot:reindex_party_search_facts

Index Roles:
rake sunspot:reindex_roles

Stop Solr server:
rake sunspot:solr:stop  


Gem Dependencies
================
sunspot_rails
sunspot

